Package: textir
Title:  Inverse Regression for Text Analysis
Version: 2.0
Date: 
Author: Matt Taddy <taddy@chicagobooth.edu>
Depends: R (>= 2.15), distrom 
Suggests: MASS
Description:  A suite of tools for text  mining, implementing
	multinomial inverse regression for text analysis.  Also includes the ability to include latent `topics' in your multinomial linear model, and a minimalist partial least squares algorithm.  
Maintainer: Matt Taddy <taddy@chicagobooth.edu>
License: GPL-3
URL: http://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/matt.taddy/index.html
